                                    <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full p-3 mr-4">
                                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <h2 class="headings xl:h4 xs:h5 text-msu-deep-ocean font-bold">Use of Website</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-4">
                                    <p class="paragraph xl:p2 xs:p3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                                        You may use our website for lawful purposes only. You agree not to use the website:
                                    </p>
                                    <ul class="space-y-3 ml-6">
                                        <li class="flex items-start">
